and performance standards.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=3Mx4QgAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',10,NULL,14),(309,'Heidi (Heidi  #1-2)','Johanna Spyri, Beverly Cleary, Angelo  Rinaldi','Juvenile Fiction','Heidi was first published in 1880. A classic tale of childhood joys and friendships, it has delighted and inspired generations of children.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=PZiwQwAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',10,NULL,14),(310,'Getting Results with Curriculum Mapping','Heidi Hayes Jacobs','Education','Teachers and administrators offer concrete advice on how to get the most out of curriculum mapping in districts and schools.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=FWNuQgAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',10,NULL,14),(311,'There\'s Always Enough: The Miraculous Move of God in Mozambique','Rolland Baker, Heidi Baker','Church work with the poor','Tells the story of an adventure that began when the authors, founders of IRIS Ministries, and both natives of California, USA, answered God\'s call to minister to the poorest of the poor.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=H-AMAQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',10,NULL,14),(312,'What to Expect the First Year (What to Expect)','Heidi Murkoff, Sharon Mazel, Arlene Eisenberg, Sandee Hathaway, Mark D. Widome','Family & Relationships','Describes each stage of child development, answers questions about child care, and includes information on common childhood ailments.','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Nmj7-1leb3oC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api',10,NULL,14),(313,'The Player\'s Handbook: The Ultimate Guide on Dating and Relationships','Heidi Fleiss, Libby Keatinge','Courtship','Well-versed in the intricacies of the male psyche, the infamous Hollywood Madam offers time-tested strategies and hard-won wisdom on how to survive the love-go-round and come out on top.','http://books.google.co